Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.78,up-left,NTP,0,0,330,,{\c&H000000&}当地美食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.78,up-left,NTP,0,0,510,,{\c&H000000&}好吃到脸蛋掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.78,up-left,NTP,0,0,675,,{\c&H000000&}热水天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.78,up-left,NTP,0,0,840,,{\c&H000000&}非常非常热哟
