Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鞘是石卷市的名产
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是石卷市出身的所以这是我的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错不错~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的夸奖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是你 真的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不挑食？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不要单说好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能有更加丰富的语言表现就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下次也拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时我的心都快冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实波的圆场太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实波 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的觉得好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被导演说了只是觉得好吃并不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是「Wake Up. Girls!」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们来到了仙台的牛舌店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
